data.description: Beautiful home for sale in desirable Washington Township neighborhood! Large driveway, garage, and carport to provide parking for several cars. Major updates from 2019 including new high efficiency heater, hot water heater and A/C, as well as a new roof, stainless steel kitchen appliances, new cabinetry, waterproof vinyl flooring, and fully spray insulated attic Kitchen also includes granite countertops, matching granite island, tile backsplash and ample cabinet space. Sliding barn door off of the dining room will lead you into the family room area that has large windows illuminating the room with natural lighting from the backyard. There are three bedrooms on this level as well as the full bath. Going downstairs you will find another multipurpose room that includes a walk in closet area right outside of it. There is also a second living area, laundry room, and half bath. On this level you will have access to the garage as well as the backyard. Schedule your showing before it's too late!
